  "text": "According to these studies, and to the experimental data from our measurements, we decided to select a fixed driving voltage of 150 Vpp for the psychophysical experiments. This value corresponds to the higher value of normal force exerted on the actuators' sides and, according to preliminary psychophysical tests, was the one which showed the best performance across 10 participants [CITATION_1] ",
